OL,5, Three million people who applied for a 
OL,6, driving licence during the worst of the
OL,7, pandemic experienced major delays, a   
OL,8, report has found.                      
OL,10,FSome applicants lost jobs or income,   
OL,11,Fand suffered social isolation and      
OL,12,Fmental health problems, parliament's   
OL,13,FPublic Accounts Committee said.        
OL,15,FThe delays affected people who applied 
OL,16,Fby post or had medical conditions.     
OL,18,FThe Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency
OL,19,F(DVLA) said it had prioritised its     
OL,20,Fonline services during the pandemic.   
